---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { site } from "../data/site";

const pageTitle = `Terms of Use | ${site.brand}`;
const pageDescription = `Terms and conditions for using the ${site.brand} website. Read our rules, intellectual property rights, and liability disclaimers.`;

const lastUpdated = "July 2, 2026";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <main class="bg-[#F5F7FA] min-h-screen py-20 px-6">
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-[#dbe7f5] overflow-hidden">
      <header class="bg-[#0B1E3B] text-white p-12 md:p-20">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-6 text-white tracking-tight">Terms of Use</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg font-medium">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>
      
      <div class="p-10 md:p-16 prose prose-slate max-w-none text-[#5B6B7C] leading-relaxed">
        <p class="text-lg">Welcome to <strong>{site.brand}</strong>. By accessing this website, we assume you accept these terms and conditions. Do not continue to use {site.url} if you do not agree to take all of the terms and conditions stated on this page.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">1. License and Copyright</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise stated, {site.brand} and/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on {site.brand}. All intellectual property rights are reserved. You may access this from {site.shortName} for your own personal use subjected to restrictions set in these terms and conditions.</p>
        <p>You must not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Republish material (including product images and technical data) from {site.url} without prior written consent.</li>
          <li>Sell, rent or sub-license material from {site.brand}.</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate or copy material from {site.brand}.</li>
          <li>Redistribute content from {site.brand}.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">2. Product Specifications</h2>
        <p>All product information, including Technical Data Sheets (TDS) and specifications provided on this website, are for reference only. While we strive for accuracy, Weifang Tianyuan Waterproof Material Co., Ltd. reserves the right to modify product specifications without prior notice based on R&D and manufacturing improvements.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">3. User Comments</h2>
        <p>Certain parts of this website offer users the opportunity to post and exchange opinions and information in certain areas of the website. {site.shortName} does not filter, edit, publish or review Comments prior to their presence on the website. Comments reflect the views and opinions of the person who posts their views and opinions.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">4. Hyperlinking to our Content</h2>
        <p>The following organizations may link to our Website without prior written approval:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Government agencies;</li>
          <li>Search engines;</li>
          <li>News organizations;</li>
          <li>Online directory distributors.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">5. Disclaimer of Liability</h2>
        <p>The information on this website is provided on an "as is" basis. To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, we exclude all representations, warranties and conditions relating to our website and the use of this website. We will not be liable for any loss or damage of any nature arising from the use of technical information provided on the site.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0B1E3B] mt-10 mb-4">6. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the People's Republic of China, and you irrevocably submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Weifang, Shandong Province.</p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>
